data.title: Austin Powers : 3-film collection
data.text:
Summary:

Secret agent Austin Powers is thawed back into action after being frozen for thirty years. The time-warped swinger has to battle again with his archenemy Dr. Evil and stop his plot to control the world; Dr. Evil travels back to 1969 and steals Austin's "mojo". Now Austin must return to the 60's to recover his mojo and stop his arch enemy from liquidating the world; Dr. Evil and Mini-me escape from prison and team up with Goldmember to kidnap Austin Power's father; now Austin has to travel back to Goldmember's time, 1975, to save him.
